    Sun–Jupiter Transit Spectra Simulation¶

    This notebook simulates the transmission spectrum and Doppler signals of a Sun–Jupiter transit using the SOAP framework and PHOENIX stellar atmosphere models.

    # Compute transit duration and ingress/egress duration

tr_ingress_egress=1./np.pi * np.arcsin(1./a *np.sqrt((1.-Rp)**2.-a**2. *np.cos(np.radians(ip))**2.))
